<item>
            <title>[SENTRY-1897] Rename sentry property to provide the list of sentry servers</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SENTRY-1897</link>
                <project id="12314720" key="SENTRY">Sentry (Retired)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Starting with Sentry 2.0, we start to support HA and thus the need to provide a comma separated list of sentry servers in the configuration. It is better to use a new property name for this. (Note: This breaks the compatibility with older 1.x Sentry releases)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
